: none !important; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: #000000; =
border-bottom-style: solid; background-color: #ccc;"> merger agreement will=
 say</a>=C2=A0something like =E2=80=9Cthe Company will not =E2=80=A6=C2=A0c=
reate, incur, assume, guarantee, endorse, suffer to exist or otherwise be l=
iable with respect to any indebtedness for borrowed money.=E2=80=9D Between=
 signing of the merger agreement and closing, the target company can=E2=80=
=99t go around borrowing money without your permission. That would change t=
he deal.</p>
